title: Anchor House Foundation Ride for Runaways
Tour of Colts Neck
course: 3.8 mile rolling loop on country roads.
registration:
On line registration.   BIKEREG.COM
Day of race registration starts 7.15 AM at ballfield on Laird Road Colts Neck.
notes:
No Feeding.  Rolling Closure.  Yellow Line Rules.  No Free Lap.  No Following Vehicles except official race vehicles.
50 field limit for Cat 5 race.  NO WAIT LISTS.  
Sub Juniors ride different course to Juniors. Starting at  same time !
First race 8AM.  Following races start at completion of previous event.  Junior race may be on course same time as Cat. 5. because of time constraints.
Colts neck residents race for free. 
Master 45-55.  2 minute delay start.
Women 1-2-3  and Women 4.  2 minute delay start.
directions: Garden State Parkway exit 109.  WEST on Rt. 520.  1 1/4 miles to PHALANX RD.  Left on PHALANX  2 miles to LAIRD Rd.  RIGHT on LAIRD  1/4 Mile to registration at ballfield on LEFT.
